<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.9.6">
<l>māyaṉeṉ ṉeñci ṉuḷḷāṉ maṟṟum yavarkku matuvē</l>
<l>kāyamuñ cīvaṉun tāṉē kālu meriyu mavaṉē</l>
<l>cēya ṉaṇiyaṉ yavarkkuñ cintaikkuṅ kōcara mallaṉ</l>
<l>ṟūyaṉ ṟuyakkaṉ mayakka ṉeṉṉuṭait tōḷiṇai yāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The Dark one is in my heart. It is not for anybody else.</l>
<l>Body and soul is he. Wind and fire is he.</l>
<l>Far is he, near is he, he no sense object for anyone’s thoughts.</l>
<l>The pure, sorrow[-bringing], confusing one is by my shoulder pair.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
